title: Processes can be unsafely terminated.
pid: 8e14ed25-11f6-4d2c-a666-872dcac6f9e5
body: |2-
  from time import sleep
  from multiprocessing import Process

  class MyProcess (Process):
    def run(self):
      while True:
        print("I'm the MyProcess.")
        sleep (0.5)

  def go():
    mt = MyProcess()
    mt.start()
    sleep(2)
    mt.terminate()
